comment: Carroll (TOR) has his hand touching Hayward's (UTA) hip but he removes it as the jump shot goes up.
Hayward (UTA) and DeRozan (TOR) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
[Observable in production angle] LHH shows Gobert (UTA) makes contact with DeRozan's (TOR) wrist on his drive and before his shot.
Favors (UTA) jumps vertically and legally contests DeRozan's (TOR) driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends DeRozan's (TOR) drive to the basket.
Toronto is correctly assessed a Delay Of Game for not exiting the timeout.
Scola (TOR) is still sliding to his left when Favors (UTA) begins his upward shooting motion.
Gobert (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he hedges on the perimeter.
Gobert (UTA) jumps vertically and maintains legal guarding position as he defends Lowry's (TOR) driving layup attempt.
LHH shows that Gobert (UTA) cleanly strips the ball from DeRozan (TOR).
Carroll (TOR) commits a take foul on Burke (UTA).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a 2 point field goal by Scola (TOR) was upheld.
Scola (TOR) commits a take foul on Favors (UTA).
